<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1040076" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo, Fautori et Cognato suo Charissimo
      <lb/><abbr><choice><orig>DN.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></orig><reg>Dn.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></reg></choice></abbr> <rs type="person"><choice><orig>NICOLAO</orig><reg>Nicolao</reg></choice> <choice><orig>BERNOULLIO</orig><reg>Bernoullio</reg></choice></rs><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <abbr>Math<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></abbr> <abbr>Pr<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></abbr> <rs type="place">Pad<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></rs></salute>
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person">Benedictus Stehelius</rs><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> <abbr>M. D.</abbr></opener>
  
<p><lb/>Si quod officium meum fuit, jam pridem non
  <lb/>sum exsequutus, Cognate charissime, occasione m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>s<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mortis, Venerandi <abbr>Dni.</abbr> <rs type="person">Parentis</rs> Tui,
  <lb/>id neutiquam factum est quod Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> a nobis ab<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sentia a memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quicquam eorum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>Tibi debeo et libenter debere sentio detriverit.
  <lb/>Sed <del><gap/></del>in causa fuit partim quod crediderim
  <lb/><add>ali<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>m</add> locum esse dandum justo isto dolori Tuo, <choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>m
  <lb/>ex decessu Tanti <rs type="person">Parentis</rs> sensurum Te pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>videb<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>.
  <lb/>Scio etenim quantum sit <del><gap/></del><rs type="person">Patrem</rs>, rem nobis
  <lb/>charissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <choice><sic>longinguis</sic><corr>longinquis</corr></choice> in regionibus semoto, nulla
  <lb/>amplius revidendi spe amittere. Scio, inquam<supplied>,</supplied>
  <lb/>quant<choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> adhuc magis dolorifica debeat esse
  <lb/>ejusmodi amissio, quo<del><gap/></del> plures in<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>amisso emicuerunt dotes. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vero In Defuncto
  <lb/>Tuo <rs type="person">Parente</rs> tant<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerunt, ut nonsolum a
  <lb/>consanguineis et amicis, sed etiam ab omnibus
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quis et cordatis Viris su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>e <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimaretur.
  <lb/>Omnes enim sciunt <choice><orig>quâ<add>nta</add></orig><reg>quanta</reg></choice> sinceritate, qua<add>nta</add> Prudenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice><supplied>,</supplied> 
  <pb facs="1040077" n="2"/> 
  <lb/>qua<add>nta</add> soliditate Judicii, quanta in muneribus
  <lb/>suis administrandis fide et Justitia fuerit
  <lb/>ornatus, aliis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> bene multis dotibus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>nemini magis cognit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> esse debent, quam Tibi.
  <lb/>Partim quod a Charissimo <rs type="person">Fratre</rs> Tuo intellexe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ram, fasciculum <rs type="letter">litterarum</rs> Tuorum <rs type="person">Amicor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
  <lb/>ad Te scriptarum nimium jam increvisse.
  <lb/>Quoniam vero haud dubito <del><gap/></del>Tuos <rs type="person">Amicos</rs>
  <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictos dolori Tuo atroci solamina
  <lb/>necessaria, simul<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Tuam ipsiusmet animi
  <lb/>fortitudinem jamjam attulisse; hinc h<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>c
  <lb/>occasione quod Illi melius abs<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> omni dubio
  <lb/>exsequuti sunt quam ego nunc <add>exsequi</add> possem, non
  <lb/>ero illa in re prolixior. Sed unicum quod ista
  <lb/>occasione faciam, est ut Deum intentis
  <lb/>precibus venerer, ut hunc casum non Tibi
  <lb/>minus, quam nobis <rs type="place">Patri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></rs> <choice><orig>[</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>ob paucitatem
  <lb/>Tuo <rs type="person">Parenti</rs> Defuncto similium<choice><orig>]</orig><reg>)</reg></choice>, tristissimum,
  <lb/>nulla ope humana mutandum, Tantisundi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>in Te et Tuam totam lectissimam familiam
  <lb/>collatis beneficiorum et felicitatum cumulis
  <lb/>velit resarcire, ut luctus vester aliquo modo
  <lb/>lenia<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, <rs type="person">Matrem</rs> Tuam honoratissimam
  <lb/>diutissime salvam et ab ulteriori m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>causa remotam conservare quam diutissime, 
  <pb facs="1040078" n="3"/> 
  <lb/>simul<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> benevolenter concedere ut annus, Professio<add><choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></add>
  <lb/>Tua tam tristibus auspiciis inchoata, felicissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>et omnibus modis prosperum processum et exit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>assequantur, Te<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> omnibus felicitatum generibus
  <lb/>quas tam bene jam diu mereris cumulare, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>efficere ut salvus Tuos identidem rursus amplecti
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>redux possis, <add>ut</add> damnum<del><gap/></del> quod <rs type="place">Patria</rs> et
  <lb/>Amici in Venerando Tuo <rs type="person">Parente</rs> passi sumus
  <lb/>in Te resarcitum <del><gap/></del>sentiamus. Ceterum dici vix
  <lb/>potest quant<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> cum voluptate ex Tuis didicerim
  <lb/>Te professionem Tuam omnium applausu inaugura<unclear reason="lost">ss</unclear>e
  <lb/>Te<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> celebre vestrum nomen Gentilitium mirif<unclear reason="lost">ice</unclear>
  <lb/>ornare, utinam l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quam ex ista re capiunt
  <lb/>omnes Tui <rs type="person">amici</rs> diutius frui potuisset Dominus
  <lb/><rs type="person">Parens</rs> Tuus. <rs type="person">Parentes</rs> mei qui Te plurimum
  <lb/>salutari volunt, in eadem mecum Tui gratia
  <lb/>vota descendunt, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue <rs type="person">Pater</rs> meus qui, nisi
  <lb/>variis admodum negotiis fuisset et esset adhucd<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>districtus ipsemet officium suum Tibi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stasset jam
  <lb/>pridem, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stabit vero quam proxime. <abbr>Dnum</abbr>
  <lb/>Tuum Consobrinum <rs type="person">Nicolaum</rs> pluribus verbis
  <lb/>salutes rogo, simul<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> an apud Vos in Anatomicis
  <lb/>aliquid edisci possit, mihi <del><gap/></del><add>quando</add> tuo co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odo fieri poterit
  <lb/>significare at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Domin<del><gap/></del><add>o</add> <rs type="person">Morgagno</rs> quando sese
  <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>buerit occasio <rs type="person">Parentis</rs> mei, mea<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> tenuia officia
  <lb/><rs type="place">his in oris</rs> offerre <add>haud dedigneris.</add> </p><closer><choice><orig>VALE</orig><reg>Vale</reg></choice> Interim Consobrine Charissime<supplied>,</supplied>
    <lb/>quam optime et me Tibi proporro <choice><sic>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>edatum</sic><corr>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatum</corr></choice> habere perge.
    <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Basil<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1717-02-20">XX. <abbr>Febr.</abbr> 1717</date>.</dateline>
    <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1717-03-13">13. <abbr>Mart.</abbr></date></foreign></note>
  <pb facs="1040079" n="4"/> 
  <address>
<addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
    <addrLine>Monsieur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Bernoulli</rs> Professeur</addrLine>
    <addrLine>en Mathemati<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> tres Celebre</addrLine>
    <addrLine>à <rs type="place">Padoüe</rs></addrLine>
</address></closer>
